snippet.title: AMBER HEARD PARODY- SOCIAL MEDIA CRINGE- IG POSTS
snippet.description:
Hello! my name is Carla Yang and Welcome to my channel!

Today's video is an Amber heard parody, based on some of her social media posts (IG posts)

Shutout to Doctor Soup and Ehacker, two very active content creators here on YouTube who report on the JD and AH case and who have also been a source of inspiration.

Disclaimer: this video was created for entertainment purposes only. 
Please check full disclaimer on video.

Thanks so much for watching!
Stay tuned, and stay safe out there!

ehackers videos:
